@非去来今<br>
多谢回复，但我的确是在编辑问题时点击“ Insert an image&quot;插入图像的URL的，不是它右边的那个超连链ICON。我刚才又试了一下，结果还是同样。即使我用一个非常短的图像URL， 比如https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/11226908-3x2-940x627.jpg， 从“Insert an image&quot;进去放在问题文本里面结果也一样，仍然只显示URL而不是它指示的图片（查看本回答的HTML source 仍然是 &quot;&lt;a href=&quot;<a href="https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/11226908-3x2-940x627.jpg" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/11226908-3x2-940x627.jpg</a>&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/11226908-3x2-940x627.jpg&lt;/a&gt;)<br>
&nbsp;：<a href="https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/11226908-3x2-940x627.jpg" rel="nofollow noreferrer noopener" target="_blank"><img src="https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/11226908-3x2-940x627.jpg" alt="https://www.abc.net.au/news/image/11226908-3x2-940x627.jpg" style="max-width:100%"></a>
